Hospital CEO Janet Compton has launched a public appeal to track down the mystery 10-year-old child.

'This is such wonderful, honest feedback from one of our young patients who has had a positive experience at Northern Health,' Ms Compton said.

'I would like to meet with this young person and thank them for their feedback.'

